show.description: Vidhi, a spirited woman shackled by secrets, finds herself trapped in a marriage of convenience with Varun Acharya, a wheelchair-bound billionaire hiding a devastating truth. What begins as a deal for survival turns into a storm of betrayal, revenge, and rediscovered strength as Vidhi battles manipulative relatives, buried pasts, and her own heart — only to rise as the unlikely pillar behind an empire. Watch Now!
